    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"no-strings-on-me\">No Strings on Me</h3><p>The Polendina are not a \"clan\" in the traditional sense-- they serve as an example of synthetic Shinobi, crafted by Schnee clan enterprises in the Land of Snow, based in part off the Hidden Sand's puppet designs. The Polendina have begun to step outside the command of their creators though, asserting their existence as true ninja, not simply another tool.</p><h4 id=\"polendina-traits\">Polendina Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Int, +1 Con <br /><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet. <br /><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Crafting, Ninshou</p>",
